OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBanks summoned on mortgages
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter rates rise shock     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Banks and building societies are       
OL,6, meeting Chancellor Jeremy Hunt as      
OL,7, pressure grows on them to help people  
OL,8, struggling with rising mortgage costs. 
OL,10,FThe meeting comes after Thursday's     
OL,11,Fshock decision by the Bank of England  
OL,12,Fto hike rates to 5%, up from 4.5%, as  
OL,13,Fit tries to tackle inflation.          
OL,15,FMillions of UK households will see     
OL,16,Ftheir budgets squeezed as a result.    
OL,18,FBut Mr Hunt and Prime Minister Rishi   
OL,19,FSunak have dismissed suggestions that  
OL,20,Fthe government should step in.         
